Teak O

Teak O
is O
a O
close O
grained O
hardwood O
with O
a O
high O
natural O
oil O
content O
. O
This O
makes O
it O
hard O
wearing O
, O
highly O
resistant O
to O
rotting O
and O
almost O
impervious O
to O
the O
effects O
of O
sun O
, O
rain O
, O
frost O
or O
snow O
. O
These O
characteristics O
combine O
to O
make O
it O
the O
ideal O
timber O
for O
all O
outdoor O
applications O
. O
Only O
premium O
grade O
plantation O
grown O
teak O
is O
used O
for O
the O
manufacture O
of O
Gloster O
furniture O
. O
The O
features O
of O
premium O
grade O
teak O
are O
a O
straight O
grain O
structure O
, O
the O
absence O
of O
knots O
, O
splits O
or O
cracks O
and O
an O
even O
overall O
colour O
. O

INDOOR O
USE O

Gloster O
buffed O
teak O
benefits O
from O
an O
enhanced O
surface O
preparation O
procedure O
, O
where O
the O
natural O
oils O
already O
contained O
within O
the O
teak O
are O
brought O
to O
the O
surface O
and O
burnished O
to O
produce O
a O
rich O
sheen O
and O
a O
consistent O
colour O
. O
If O
you O
intend O
to O
use O
your O
furniture O
indoors O
or O
under O
cover O
outside O
where O
it O
will O
not O
get O
wet O
, O
the O
teak O
will O
retain O
much O
of O
its O
original O
colour O
and O
the O
soft O
sheen O
of O
its O
buffed O
finish O
. O
Any O
marks O
, O
stains O
or O
damage O
to O
the O
buffed O
teak O
finish O
can O
be O
restored O
using O
the O
Gloster O
Buffed O
Teak O
Repair O
Kit O
. O

OUTDOOR O
USE O

Gloster O
buffed O
teak O
benefits O
from O
an O
enhanced O
surface O
preparation O
procedure O
, O
where O
the O
natural O
oils O
already O
contained O
within O
the O
teak O
are O
brought O
to O
the O
surface O
and O
burnished O
to O
produce O
a O
rich O
sheen O
and O
a O
consistent O
colour O
. O

As O
with O
natural O
finish O
teak O
, O
left O
to O
age O
naturally O
outside O
, O
buffed O
teak O
will O
gradually O
change O
to O
a O
soft O
, O
silver O
grey O
as O
the O
pigments O
in O
the O
surface O
layer O
of O
