to O
water O
, O
you O
should O
also O
expect O
the O
surface O
grain O
to O
rise O
slightly O
. O
As O
a O
part O
of O
the O
buffing O
process O
, O
the O
surface O
is O
wetted O
before O
final O
sanding O
to O
raise O
the O
grain O
, O
so O
there O
will O
be O
significantly O
less O
raised O
grain O
on O
buffed O
teak O
than O
on O
natural O
finish O
teak O
. O
We O
recommend O
that O
you O
allow O
your O
teak O
furniture O
to O
weather O
naturally O
this O
way O
and O
simply O
clean O
thoroughly O
once O
or O
twice O
a O
year O
with O
our O
Teak O
Cleaner O
. O
Buffed O
teak O
