furniture O
as O
this O
will O
erode O
the O
surface O
. O

Because O
teak O
is O
a O
naturally O
oily O
wood O
, O
it O
is O
not O
possible O
to O
paint O
or O
varnish O
. O
Any O
paint O
or O
varnish O
applied O
will O
not O
adhere O
properly O
to O
the O
surface O
and O
after O
a O
