on O
a O
regular O
maintenance O
programme O
as O
Teak O
Sealer O
needs O
to O
be O
regularly O
re O
applied O
to O
provide O
continuous O
protection O
. O

If O
you O
intend O
to O
store O
your O
furniture O
over O
the O
winter O
, O
